CU Boulder FCQ Analysis



About

This project examines the FCQ data provided by CU boulder.

As CU upperclassmen, we have now spent many hours stressing over which classes to pick, and what to expect from the course. Which courses are actually difficult? Who are the ‘best’ professors? When should I take a certain course? What combination of courses should I take? → These questions drove us to begin exploring CU’s FCQ data. → Could our answers lie there?

Dashboard 1 instructions/more details: we can analyze the relation between instructor and avg course

Dashboard 2 instructions/more details: we focus on instructors and see which cluster they belongs to
